---
title: Golden Breaded Chicken with Sweet Potato Wedges and Honey Mustard
description: A twist on a simple chicken dinner that the whole family will love. Sweet and zesty honey mustard is a delicious dip for tender breaded chicken and sweet potatoes alike. Do your kiddos love chicken fingers? Thickly cut the chicken into sticks they can grab, dip and devour.
